			<h2>Introduction</h2>
			<p>I've started working on what I'm calling 'KingVideo' while in development because of my frustrations with YouTube and how they deal with content creators. Orignally I wished to create a site where myself and a few friends could upload videos and share them with everyone (from my own server) but after learning of the technical requirements of a project that scale I decided to refine my goals into something more managable and possible with my low budget.</p> 

			<p>One of my goals is to create a site that is as distraction free as possible so that the viewers can watch the content without anything else getting in the way, no ads, no suggested videos that you're not interested in on the side and so forth.</p>

			<p>For more information on the goals and plans please keep reading</p>
