			<h2>Watching</h2>
			<p>Watching videos is clearly the primary goal of the project. I wanted a way to share MY videos with my viewers away from YouTube and still be able to package it into a clean format that is less derpy than PlayLists. </p> 
			<p>I've also decided for this project I want a number of features to be possible, such as password protected videos. In addition I also would like to do more with the "private" video feature there is on YouTube though I'm not sure how or what that'll be yet. </p>
			<p>I would love to do my own custom player for videos that will eventually be hosted from my own service, but for now the videos will be embedded from guess who? YouTube and played from their servers.</p>
